{
  "stem": "1873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe on the way they will-- still hope.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But half way in this, in this corridor, they realized, probably, that they are going to die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what's happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will come to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day Frenzel called me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eh, Kleine, come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Little one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took me from the-- probably they need people-- took me from my fireplace, from the place I was working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they give me a rake, and told me to go and clean up the hallway, this corridor, because the next 500 people were coming.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was raking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you must do everything perfect because the terror was so terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You rake, and the Germans still see like, a piece of paper, they would shot you for it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very careful, but I've seen something when I was raking the sand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something was going between the teeth of the rake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I bent down-- little piece of paper-- I picked up some paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I look close, and it was money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if we talk about the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In our 20th century, we talk about a resistance, we associate resistance with guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was a spiritual resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Imagine going to do death and still sabotaging, knowing they will die, taking the time and ripped the paper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so little pieces should be of no use to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is really heroism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I was-- I've seen many cases, different cases of such act.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I've seen different Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, as I said, I could talk day and night, but we must move on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we start to organize.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a few cases where a bigger group of people tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it did partially-- it was [INAUDIBLE] came partially it wasn't. they were caught.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
